reviewText: Too funny!  Wish it was still on TV.
wish this had several more seasons i really enjoy bob and margaret....
My crazy cartoon obsession. I love it!
These characters are funny you can see yourself or someone you know.

What's to say? I love Bob and Margaret. Drolly funny! Great British humor. Somebody needs to get with it and provide ALL the episodes on dvd, not just season 1 or two >_< (and in the North American format!)
I bought these 2 episodes on VHS(!) because I have execrable internet and I cannot download or stream movies. Luckily I still have a vhs player ;p
Oh and yeah, if you've got this far you know that these aren't kiddies' cartoons but made for grownups to enjoy, not that there is anything shocking in Bob and Margaret.
Lovers of the droll, sublime and mundane untie!

I just like there life style a little bit of everything such a cute couple, almost gentle,so loving just cute..
And this is the review for all three season.

Smart and funny, I loved this cartoon when it was on and I'm so glad i found it and can watch it here. Miss them in England and really miss Bob's old voice, this one is a bit nasally. Love the cartoon though.

Love bob & Margaret series. So funny & entertaining. Started watching one and couldn't stop..lol
Well worth the price. love it so much i have bought all the seasons. Pure good hearted entertainment.
